reviewText: I have owned/viewed all of the Playboy Celebrity Centerfold videos and I firmly believe Patti Davis has the best one of all.She shows the most confidence of all the other celebs. Her tricep tone, flat abs and understated make-up; even though she isn't amply endowed, her pert nips add to my 4-Star rating. I would have given the video a 5 but I thought the editting, for that matter, the editting on the others wasn't any better. Playboy must hire new-be editors or underpay their experienced ones.

reviewText: Playboy - Patti Davis Celebrity Centerfold is fifty minutes and was released on April 30, 2002. As for as celebrities goes, non-Playmates, she is the most liberated of them all. I have own LaToya Jackson, Jessica Hahn, and a few others and you had to wait for the nudity or there was very little nudity. In her opening scene she is emerging from the lake nude. With the exception of the Power Plant segment, she is fully nude in all other segments. Basically Patti talks a little bit about herself, growing up as a Reagan, and her take on feminism. The only downside to the video is the Playmate Profile on Victoria Zdrok (Playboy Playmate of the Month for October 1994, Penthouse Pet of the Month June 2002, and Penthouse Pet of the Year 2004); she shows very little nudity as compared to Patti who is fully nude in most of her segments. Below are segments of Patti and Victoria.PattiPower Plant-Does a slow striptease; her underwear stays on. This segment goes for an artistic scenario.Sculpted Bodies-She is 100 percent nude from start to finish of the segment.Romantic Beach-Patti starts off topless only wearing a lei and skirt. After about thirty seconds later the skirt is gone and she is nude.Angel-About thirty seconds into the segment she is totally nude.Kick Boxing-The segment switches back and forth from her kick boxing workout to scenes of her in the nude.Near Future-Starts off dressed in black. Patti along with another guy and female have a three-way.VictoriaLibrary-She strip in the library, but not one scene shows her in the nude.Vargas-Very, very, very little nudity and boring.Zarina-Full nudity for about 15% of the segment.If you got rid the Victoria Zdrok part of the DVD then this would be a great video.
